*Chiarello & Klein, (2004) ''DC Comics Guide to Coloring and Lettering Comics'', Watson-Guptill .
*Miller, Brian & Kristy (2008) ''Hi_Fi Color For Comics : Digital Techniques for Professional Results'', Impact.

