===Speed Wave=== The site offers a service by which groups of friends may compare results against each other and as a group average. Badges are also awarded for achievements such as ''Highest Download Speed'' and ''Lowest Latency''. Badges are awarded when either ''Highest Download'' or Lowest Ping'' will be.
===My Results=== The Ookla Speed Test also has a tool called “My Results” which lets you graphically compare your upload and download speeds as well as the different servers you have tested. Users who have been through many internet service providers, or that have more than one, may find value in this tool and could use it to choose the most efficient.
